msgstr "združljivosti mojega dodatka ni mogoče nadgraditi"

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:26
msgid "my add-on's compatibility is upgraded successfully"
msgstr "združljivost mojega dodatka je uspešno nadgrajena"

#: src/amo/utils/promoted.js:40
msgid ""
"Official add-on built by Mozilla Firefox. Meets security and performance "
"standards."
msgstr ""
"Uraden dodatek, katerega avtor je Mozilla Firefox. Izpolnjuje standarde "
"varnosti in učinkovitosti delovanja."

#: src/amo/utils/promoted.js:50
msgid ""
"Firefox only recommends add-ons that meet our standards for security and "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"Firefox priporoča samo dodatke, ki ustrezajo našim standardom glede varnosti "
"in učinkovitosti delovanja."

